welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Mashpee, a charming and picturesque town known for its rich history and beautiful natural landscapes. We invite you to explore and embrace all that our city has to offer during your stay. Enjoy your time in Mashpee!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Barnstable Airport handles all commercial flights and includes a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Barnstable Airport is used for private and charter flights, as well as flight training and other aviation services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Martha's Vineyard Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Martha's Vineyard Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Private Terminal

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.
